Dialogue: 3,0:00:01.62,0:00:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an exciting memory of mine where Morishima-senpai and I went to a family restaurant one day, after school.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:10.75,0:00:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened a few days before Christmas.
