Dialogue: 3,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tachibana-kun?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:24.74,0:00:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem really uneasy for some reason.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually having tea with you in a family restaurant, Morishima-senpai...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm really grateful!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:37.44,0:00:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be grateful for that!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:41.19,0:00:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is something that would never happen to me...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it actually is happening...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:47.40,0:00:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I just can't believe it!  I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:50.78,0:00:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're making it such a big deal!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:57.63,0:01:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that I can have tea with Senpai...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we had to come to where Kaoru works, of all places...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:03.78,0:01:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen if she sees this?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:08.28,0:01:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:13.10,0:01:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, have you decided on what you'd like?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:16.30,0:01:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:18.38,0:01:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Tachibana-kun, are you okay with eating sweet stuff?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, to a normal extent.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:25.40,0:01:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... will you share a parfait with me?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A parfait?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:34.92,0:01:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:36.32,0:01:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:38.60,0:01:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I take your order?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:41.85,0:01:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana-kun, can we?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:44.19,0:01:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:48.49,0:01:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it wasn't Kaoru.
