Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:01.22,RestaurantTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.3\an4\frz17.048\pos(363,347)}Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:01.22,RestaurantTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.3\an4\frz17.048\pos(439,373)}Totosu
Dialogue: 3,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the one that girl's carrying.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:06.15,0:02:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, it's Kaoru!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:08.91,0:02:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana-kun, do you know her?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  She's my classmate.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:14.31,0:02:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:15.92,0:02:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So students from our school actually work here.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:21.57,0:02:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:23.12,0:02:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it'd be bad if she sees the two of us alone together.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:27.29,0:02:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:30.70,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I have a great idea!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:37.71,0:02:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:40.32,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nobody'll know you came with me if I hide myself like this, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, it's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun this way!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, here she comes.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:54.67,0:02:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shining Lovers Parfait!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.86,ParfaitTS3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(361,0)\pos(365,361)}Shining Lovers Parfait
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.86,ParfaitTS3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\bord5\fad(361,0)\pos(365,361)\3c&HFFFFFF&}Shining Lovers Parfait
Dialogue: 3,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yo, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:00.72,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare for customers to order this, so I was wondering who it was...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was you.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:06.81,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's right!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:09.58,0:03:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who are you having this special parfait meant for lovers with?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came with someone else, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.04,0:03:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw on your ticket.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now who could it be?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:24.08,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's totally amused by this.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Umehara.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:45.00,0:03:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I have nothing else to say!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you can come out now.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're having a parfait with Umehara-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you hid yourself, Senpai.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was interested in what excuse you'd come up with.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:11.17,0:04:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's have the Shining Lovers Parfait together.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shining Lovers Parfait I had with Senpai was delicious...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:24.99,0:04:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I get the feeling I lost something...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas will arrive soon.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:33.20,0:04:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can spend a happy\NChristmas with Morishima-senpai?
