Dialogue: 3,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru said she has a shift today.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't disturb her, so I guess I'll go straight home.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:59.88,0:05:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go read books in the bookstore!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost Christmas.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A date with Kaoru, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a Christmas cake?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:14.56,0:05:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking orders!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.71,0:05:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Christmas cakes are delicious!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:29.07,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I was thinking of going to the bookstore for a bit...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your costume...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:36.24,0:05:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obviously a Santa costume.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:41.88,0:05:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?  Is there a problem?!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for my job, so I had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:58.08,ShopDTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax0.3\move(510,253,435,253,0,9996)\frz338.352}Shopping\NDistrict
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:58.08,ShopDTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fax-0.2\frz8.321\c&HEBF2DE&\move(162,285,87,285)}Sale
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:58.08,ShopDTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fax0.7\frz330.348\c&HB1B3B2&\move(601,351,526,351)}Sale
Dialogue: 3,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you quit your job at the family restaurant?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.  This is just a temp job.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pays well.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, how many jobs are you working?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That many?!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:07.04,0:06:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who might become my\Nnew dad said the same thing you did.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:13.56,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that I didn't have to work.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you gonna stop?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still thinking.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:23.69,0:06:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where do you think you're looking?!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:32.61,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking your Santa hat with cat ears is really cute!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.58,0:06:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar, that wasn't where you were looking!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was somewhere lower down!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... uh...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perv.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.89,0:06:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll buy one, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this cake for the cheapest price of 2,500 yen.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a loss-incurring discount!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:56.10,0:07:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that price is too low for viewing my costume.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:00.79,0:07:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your loss-incurring discount.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:07.23,0:07:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling cold from wearing so little?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi, pay me back with your body.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me finish selling these.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:18.67,0:07:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer do you want me\Nto stand here in such cold weather?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a Christmas cake?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:27.89,0:07:30.83,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still taking orders!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:29.40,0:07:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're delicious!  Would you like one?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:31.48,0:07:34.38,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a Christmas cake?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like one?  They're delicious!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care in carrying them.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for buying!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sold them all!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viewing your costume is pretty pricey.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:51.48,0:07:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't anywhere near enough to pay for it.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:57.26,0:08:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my fill of looking at Kaoru in a Santa suit.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:01.62,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I should ask where she'd like to go for our Christmas date.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:07.20,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe I should talk to him about our Christmas plans.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:22.72,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go home now?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:27.18,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... right.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:32.67,0:08:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-See you.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:46.76,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to Christmas!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be sick on Christmas!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
