Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:07.52,ArcTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.1\pos(236,164)\3c&H6F6CE1&}Nakata Sae Chapter
Dialogue: 3,0:09:08.31,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something trivial that happened one December night.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:14.45,0:09:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day was an important anniversary for the boy.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's home.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:23.88,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  That day was his birthday.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:28.16,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he returned home, neither his family\Nnor a birthday cake was anywhere to be found.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:35.79,0:09:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy, disappointed that he'd have to spend his birthday alone, quietly shut himself in his closet.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:44.42,0:09:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.63,0:09:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been abandoned by my family and my goddess of luck anyway.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:04.73,0:10:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl was standing before the boy.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:08.56,0:10:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the goddess of luck\Nhad not abandoned the boy just yet.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sae-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:15.59,0:10:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry for visiting so late.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?  Are you looking for Miya?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, she's not at home.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm not.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:26.19,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for S-Se... no, I-Instructor...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:31.95,0:10:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... uh...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:43.64,0:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know it's my birthday?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:46.97,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Miya-chan told me.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:51.29,0:10:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... here's your present.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A present?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:56.33,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.  It's nothing grand, though...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.65,0:11:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be cold.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.00,0:11:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry there isn't much to do, since nobody else is home.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:19.83,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.90,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's phrase, "nobody else is home",\Nresounded in the girl's head and sent her heart racing.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:30.87,0:11:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nobody's home", "Nobody's home", "Alone together"...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.79,0:11:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:41.04,0:11:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you aren't the type to commit foul play.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I open it?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A book?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  An album?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:56.27,0:12:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl's first birthday present to the boy turned out to be quite the curveball.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:02.81,0:12:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, it was a risky high-inside pitch.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:09.16,0:12:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an upper-diagonal pitch that far exceeded the boy's imagination.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"W-What is this?"
Dialogue: 3,0:12:16.84,0:12:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wooh!", the boy gave a masculine roar in his heart.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:21.97,0:12:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is... Sae-chan's...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...swimsuit photo, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:35.08,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sae-chan's qipao photo, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:42.95,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Sae-chan's nurse photo, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:48.60,0:12:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Sae-chan's miniskirt policewoman photo, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:52.99,0:12:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is a melting pot of excitement!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:57.73,0:13:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Sae-chan's n-n-negligee photo, right?!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:04.53,0:13:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's thoughts had gone completely berserk.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:07.74,0:13:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was now a berserk train nobody could stop.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstoppable.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:14.50,0:13:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you give this to me?!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Miya-chan about what you like, Senpai.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:21.88,0:13:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that you often read photobooks of women wearing swimsuits and other stuff...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So you...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:31.54,0:13:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... it's embarrassing after all to have you see them...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:36.76,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think you look really cute in these photos.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... no!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.00,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!  Don't!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:55.54,0:13:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the boy's face was buried in the girl's breasts.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:59.81,0:14:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That warmth was the best possible present for the boy, one that warmed both his body and soul.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sae-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.81,0:14:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the present.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:17.71,0:14:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:21.06,0:14:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miya took those photos?!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:30.52,0:14:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she said she knew all about what would please you.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:37.58,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miya, you're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten more days until Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:43.24,0:14:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the Goddess of the Holy Night smile upon them both?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, Boy...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:56.55,0:14:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nii-nii liked Sae-chan's present!
